definitions.definition: A gait of a horse between a trot and a gallop , consisting of three beats and a "suspension" phase, where there are no feet on the ground. Also describing this gait on other four-legged animals.
A ride on a horse at such speed.

main_definition: A gait of a horse between a trot and a gallop , consisting of three beats and a "suspension" phase, where there are no feet on the ground. Also describing this gait on other four-legged animals.
secondary_definitions: A ride on a horse at such speed.

definitions.definition: One who cants or whines ; a beggar .
One who makes hypocritical pretensions to goodness ; one who uses canting language.

main_definition: One who cants or whines ; a beggar .
